WEBVTT

00:00:27.708 --> 00:00:31.184
And that happened just a few months
after women had gained the right

00:00:31.208 --> 00:00:33.917
to open a bank account
without their husband's signature.

00:00:35.208 --> 00:00:37.101
Just before I got on stage,

00:00:37.125 --> 00:00:38.750
a young woman approached me.

00:00:39.875 --> 00:00:41.434
"Ms. Novogratz," she said,

00:00:41.458 --> 00:00:43.476
"I think you knew my auntie."

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:44.809
"Really?

00:00:44.833 --> 00:00:46.684
What was her name?"

00:00:46.708 --> 00:00:48.167
She said, "Felicula."

00:00:49.958 --> 00:00:51.875
I could feel tears well.

00:00:52.958 --> 00:00:56.184
One of the first women
parliamentarians in the country,

00:00:56.208 --> 00:00:58.059
Felicula was a cofounder,

